author: PTI
title: Justin Timberlake: Jessica Biel and I not very good parents
text:
London: Singer Justin Timberlake does not think he and his wife Jessica Biel are "very good" at parenting this six-month-old son Silas just yet.


Jessica Biel and Justin Timberlake. Pic/AFP 
The 34-year-old singer said he and Biel, 33, are still trying to adapt to their lives as parents after welcoming their son Silas into the world six months ago, reported Female First.
Speaking at the Gay, Lesbian and Straight Education Network's Respect Awards, Timberlake said, "My beautiful wife and I are a couple of new parents. We're not very good at it yet."
The couple, who got married in 2012, were at the awards to receive their gong for Inspiration.
